text: Nuha Barrow (born 10 October 1993) is a Gambian international footballer who plays for AS Douanes, as a defender. ==Career== Born in Tujereng, he has played club football for Gamtel and AS Douanes. He made his international debut for Gambia in 2015. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Gambian footballers Category:The Gambia international footballers Category:Gamtel FC players Category:AS Douanes (Senegal) players Category:Association football defenders Category:Gambian expatriate footballers Category:Gambian expatriate sportspeople in Senegal Category:Expatriate footballers in Senegal
